			  	Because with restrictions like these you have to be around 24/7. No one will have the time to sit there and wait to take a planet. People can hoard planets, and it will take them nearly a full day to kill them making death nearly impossible once you get to high levels.<br />
<br />
This restriction only further consolidates the power of the megas, as raping is the only way to kill their members. Also as it was in Mari, you could have broken someone and only gotten one planet from it, as others would take them before you, and you would have to wait for the cool down.			   <P align=right></P>
